      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FUEL THE FIRE (1) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by one length at this track in a handy 22.00 beating Smooth Blast. The form out of last run is most impressive. Can continue on his winning ways. MADE YOU LOOK (2) was below best last time finishing eighth at this track, but prior to that had been racing well including a Grade 5 win two back at this track. Expecting sharp improvement this line-up. ASCEND KALMIA (4) has a strong record this journey with two wins and a minor from four starts. Was out of placings last time (29.48) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing sixth and beaten 12 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances. ASTON KINNIE (8) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
